address2: 7th Floor Shiv Sagar Estate Dr. Annie Besant Road, Worli
longBusinessSummary: Shree Renuka Sugars Limited manufactures and refines sugar in India and internationally. The company provides white/refined sugar, as well as molasses, bagasse, press mud, and organic manure; and ethyl alcohol from molasses, and fuel grade ethanol. It also produces power from bagasse, a sugarcane by product for state grids with total cogeneration capacity of 242 MW. The company was incorporated in 1995 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India. Shree Renuka Sugars Limited is a subsidiary of Wilmar Sugar Holdings Pte. Ltd.
